rows.label: bf11480100_0010
rows.name: What did you think?

rows.label: bf11480100_0020
rows.name: You mean, about him?

rows.label: bf11480100_0030
rows.name: Let's see...

rows.label: bf11480100_0035
rows.name:
In a word: he seemed very human.
Protecting his heart with a mask of lies.

rows.label: bf11480100_0040
rows.name: Are you curious what's behind it?

rows.label: bf11480100_0050
rows.name:
Not really. Most humans are like that,
aren't they?

rows.label: bf11480100_0060
rows.name: Cutting to the chase, I see.

rows.label: bf11480100_0070
rows.name:
But I hear his achievements in 
Acedia have been grand.

rows.label: bf11480100_0080
rows.name:
The refugee protection policies from
last year are his work, as well.

rows.label: bf11480100_0090
rows.name:
So a hypocrite, then. Isn't that what
you call the type?

rows.label: bf11480100_0100
rows.name: Quite... I hope that's all he is.

rows.label: bf11480100_0110
rows.name: He smiled. Did you notice?

rows.label: bf11480100_0120
rows.name: No.

rows.label: bf11480100_0130
rows.name: I think...he might actually be enjoying this.

rows.label: bf11480100_0140
rows.name: What?

rows.label: bf11480100_0150
rows.name: The world in this state.

rows.label: bf11480100_0160
rows.name: That's interesting...

rows.label: bf11480100_0170
rows.name:
You felt something was wrong, didn't you?
That's why you brought me.

rows.label: bf11480100_0180
rows.name: Don't you think they're worth saving?

rows.label: bf11480100_0190
rows.name: If you think they are, you know you'll have my aid.

rows.label: bf11480100_0200
rows.name: Even if you disagree?

rows.label: bf11480100_0210
rows.name: That's not for the likes of me to decide.

rows.label: bf11480100_0220
rows.name: It's up to you humans.
